    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. it's just frustrating that the nutrients seem to just disappear from the soil even though I've been fertilizing. it feels like something is actively stealing the good stuff from my plants before they can even use it. is there anything else that could be \"taking\" the nutrients away besides just the plants eating them?",
